  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot water to fire, acid to robots and pesticide to plant monsters, switch the liquids quickly and survive as long as you can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Likewise shoot beer to glass, coffee to cups and wine to chalice to fulfill the drinks in the restaurant. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eliminate the enemies and fulfill the drinks accordingly; just a mistake and game is over.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete against players globally on Steam leaderboards.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fancy achievements to decorate your profile.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/713380/extras/c96cfd86a4a6df5a44fb7f543d0d498b.avif?t=1769796559\" width=600 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot water to fire, acid to robots and pesticide to plant monsters, switch the liquids quickly and survive as long as you can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Likewise shoot beer to glass, coffee to cups and wine to chalice to fulfill the drinks in the restaurant. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eliminate the enemies and fulfill the drinks accordingly; just a mistake and game is over.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete against players globally on Steam leaderboards.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fancy achievements to decorate your profile.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/713380/extras/c96cfd86a4a6df5a44fb7f543d0d498b.avif?t=1769796559\" width=600 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
